font awsam use in web:

=> Download font awsam
=> use webfonts folder from download font awsam to project folder
=> copy all.min.css and fontawsome.min.css file to project folder into css folder
=> pip install fontawesomefree

For Django:
=> pip install fontawesomefree
=>INSTALLED_APPS = [
    'fontawesomefree'
  ]
=> <script src="{% static 'fontawesomefree/js/all.min.js' %}"></script>
=> <link href="{% static 'fontawesomefree/css/all.min.css' %}" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
